Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:00.53,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就保护他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:03.97,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这才能表现我们的坚强
