Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.69,0:47:50.46,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\a1}You've got to be strong
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.99,0:47:52.98,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\a1}It's never too late
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.91,0:47:58.15,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\a1}I never say die
